  subheadline="New parking lot construction and full-depth replacement for commercial properties in Sarasota and Sarasota County."
  intro="Manatee Concrete builds commercial parking lots in Sarasota that are engineered to last. Properly graded, reinforced concrete construction that handles heavy traffic and Florida's weather without constant maintenance."
  body={[
    "We manage the full scope — sub-base prep, forming, pour, jointing, and finish — and coordinate directly with your civil engineer and site contractor to keep the project on schedule.",
    "From small retail lots to large commercial developments, we bring the same standard of work to every project in Sarasota County."
  ]}
  bullets={[
    "Site grading & sub-base preparation",
    "Reinforced concrete slab construction",
    "Expansion joint layout & installation",
    "ADA parking space compliance",
    "Curb & gutter integration",
    "Sealing & line stripe coordination"
  ]}
  heroImage="/images/service-parking.jpg"
  heroAlt="Commercial parking lot construction in Sarasota FL"
/>
